	<li>To provide you with information, products or services that you request or otherwise elect to receive from us or from one of our strategic partners;</li>
	<li>To notify you about changes to the Service;</li>
	<li>To allow you to utilize the trip integration, sharing, and messaging features of the Service, if and when you choose to do so; and</li>
