</ul>

<h3>Disclosure of Personal Information to Third Parties</h3>
<p>We may from time-to-time make certain personal information available to strategic partners that work with the Company such as the following:</p>
<ul>
	<li>Various subsidiaries of the Company that support the Service ;</li>
